      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"withdraw and rest\" sounds nice but it kinda feels like you're just describing checking out. like, if the whole world is just going to burn anyway, is it even rational to keep fighting or even keeping up the struggle to live? it feels more like a logical conclusion than a mental health crisis. anyone who says otherwise is just lying to themselves to feel better. wouldn't it be more honest to just accept that there's no future worth staying for?",
